title: New: Tyler, The Creator x Toro y Moi – Hey You
content:
A year ago and a collaboration like this would have sent the buzz blogs into catastrophic meltdown, now with the disappointing release of GOBLIN well behind us, Tyler spitting over a Toro y Moi beat seems almost uninviting.

Thankfully, the beat in question is far more interesting than the majority of his XL released album, (Yonkers aside), although he still has little of any worth to say. It’s crass, offensive and sort of boring to tell the truth… oh well.
